ns/twitter-new.png" alt="twitter social icon" width="24" height="24" loading="lazy"/></a><a href="https://github.com/slogging?ref=hackernoon" target="_blank" rel="dofollow"><img src="/social-icons/github-new.png" alt="github social icon" width="24" height="24" loading="lazy"/></a><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/hackernoon?ref=hackernoon" target="_blank" rel="dofollow"><img src="/social-icons/linkedin-new.png" alt="linkedin social icon" width="24" height="24" loading="lazy"/></a></div><div style="margin-top:20px;display:flex"><a class="sc-ca135b0f-2 csJLvi">About @<!-- -->slogging</a></div></div></div><p class="paragraph">Do you remember what you were doing in 2016? Sergiu Craitoiu does!<br/>Welcome Sergiu Craitoiu to the Hackernoon Slogging AMA! Since 2016, Sergiu and the team at Alien Pixel Studios have been working on the new game Unbound; Worlds Apart which recently launched on Steam and Nintendo Switch. </p><p class="paragraph">This <a href="http://slogging.com/?ref=hackernoon.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer ugc">Slogging</a> thread by Akasha Rose, Justin Roberti, Limarc Ambalina, Sergiu Craitoiu, JeffreyHarris, Karma, Jose Hernandez, Jack Boreham and Nicolas Ng occurred in slogging&#x27;s official #amas channel, and has been edited for readability.</p><div class="not-paragraph"><div class="slogging flex-1 flex flex-col bg-white overflow-hidden"><div class="px-6 py-4 flex-1 overflow-y-scroll"><div class="slack flex items-start mb-4 text-3xl"><div class="mr-3"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:relative;max-width:100%"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;max-width:100%"><img style="display:block;max-width:100%;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0" alt="" aria-hidden="true" 