gnup" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">Signup</a></li><li class="sc-735f3d4c-5 iwcsEh"><a href="http://techbrief.hackernoon.com" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">Tech Brief</a></li><li class="sc-735f3d4c-5 iwcsEh"><a href="http://hackernoon.com/tagged" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">Tech Tags</a></li><li class="sc-735f3d4c-5 iwcsEh"><a href="http://hackernoon.com/tagged/hackernoon-top-story" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">Top Stories</a></li></ul></div><div class="sc-735f3d4c-2 vAUey"><h2 class="sc-735f3d4c-3 chbRld"><a href="https://app.hackernoon.com/new" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">WRITE</a></h2><ul class="sc-735f3d4c-4 dTLxOr"><li class="sc-735f3d4c-5 iwcsEh"><a href="https://help.hackernoon.com/distribution" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">Distribution</a></li><li class="sc-735f3d4c-5 iwcsEh"><a href="https://help.hackernoon.com/use-our-editor" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">Editor Tips</a></li><li class="sc-735f3d4c-5 iwcsEh"><a href="https://help.hackernoon.com/editorial-guideline" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">Guidelines</a></li><li class="sc-735f3d4c-5 iwcsEh"><a href="http://app.hackernoon.com/new" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">New Story</a></li><li class="sc-735f3d4c-5 iwcsEh"><a href="https://help.hackernoon.com/writer-account--perks" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">Perks</a></li><li class="sc-735f3d4c-5 iwcsEh"><a href="https://help.hackernoon.com/writing-prompts" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">Prompts</a></li><li class="sc-735f3d4c-5 iwcsEh"><a href="https://hackernoon.com/why-i-write-on-hacker-noon-nl28335q" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">Why Write</a></li></ul></div><div class="sc-735f3d4c-2 vAUey"><h2 class="sc-735f3d4c-3 chbRld"><a href="https://app.hackernoon.com/brand" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">PARTNER</a></h2><ul class="sc-735f3d4c-4 dTLxOr"><li class="sc-735f3d4c-5 iwcsEh"><a href="https://sponsor.hackernoon.com/billboard" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 TRIJC">Billboard</a></li><li class="sc-735f3d4c-5 iwcsEh"><a href="https://sponsor.hackernoon.com/brand-as-author" class="sc-735f3d4c-6 T