e for hard platforms, Hollow Knight for atmosphere and monster design, Diablo 2 for lore and quests.\u003cbr/\u003eSo all those combined helped us shaped Unbound :)\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"not-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"slogging flex-1 flex flex-col bg-white overflow-hidden\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"px-6 py-4 flex-1 overflow-y-scroll\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"slack flex items-start mb-4 text-3xl\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan class=\"user font-bold mr-4\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"timestamp text-grey text-base\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e  \u003cdiv class=\"reactions\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"not-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"slogging flex-1 flex flex-col bg-white overflow-hidden\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"px-6 py-4 flex-1 overflow-y-scroll\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"slack flex items-start mb-4 text-3xl\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"mr-3\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://avatars.slack-edge.com/2021-02-03/1714122882516_6d2ae4a871511c183ba9_48.jpg\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded mr-3\"/\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan class=\"user font-bold mr-4\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://hackernoon.com/u/nicolasng\"\u003eNicolas Ng\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"timestamp text-grey text-base\"\u003eJul 29, 2021, 6:56 AM\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e  \u003cdiv class=\"reactions\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"paragraph\"\u003eHey Sergiu Craitoiu! I\u0026#x27;m wondering if you had to scrap any ideas or mechanics during the development of this game. Learning what developers had to leave on the cutting room floor is always really fascinating\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"not-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"slogging flex-1 flex flex-co